  <div class="container">
    <div class="highlight">
      <h2>📢 Important Advice Before You Begin</h2>
      <p>Preparation is key! Whether it's an interview or board exam, confidence comes from clarity. Use your time wisely and stay positive.</p>
    </div><h2>✅ Interview Tips (Job / Entry Test)</h2>
<ul>
  <li>👔 Dress professionally and arrive 15 minutes early.</li>
  <li>📄 Keep copies of your resume, ID, and certificates.</li>
  <li>💬 Practice common questions like “Tell me about yourself.”</li>
  <li>🎯 Research the company or institute before appearing.</li>
  <li>🤝 Maintain eye contact, smile confidently, and speak clearly.</li>
  <li>🧠 Don’t memorize answers, understand the concepts instead.</li>
  <li>🙋 Ask thoughtful questions at the end if allowed.</li>
</ul>

<h2>📚 Paper/Board Exam Tips</h2>
<ol>
  <li>📅 Make a realistic timetable and follow it daily.</li>
  <li>✍️ Solve past papers and practice MCQs regularly.</li>
  <li>📖 Focus more on understanding instead of rote learning.</li>
  <li>⏰ During the exam, divide your time wisely per question.</li>
  <li>🔍 Revise your answer sheet in the last 10 minutes.</li>
  <li>🧘‍♂️ Stay calm and don’t panic if you forget an answer. Skip and return later.</li>
  <li>🍎 Eat light and rest well a night before the paper.</li>
</ol>

<div class="highlight">
  <h2>🌟 Final Words from HiClass</h2>
  <p>We believe in your potential. Keep working hard, avoid distractions, and never give up. May your efforts bring you great success. 💪</p>
